{
  "video_id": "MEDgtjpycYg",
  "title": "How to speak up for yourself | Adam Galinsky",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13441.0,
      "end_time": 16588.0,
      "text": "Speaking up is hard to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16588.0,
      "end_time": 21531.0,
      "text": "I understood the true meaning of this phrase exactly one month ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21531.0,
      "end_time": 25113.0,
      "text": "when my wife and I became new parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25113.0,
      "end_time": 26815.0,
      "text": "It was an amazing moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26815.0,
      "end_time": 29024.0,
      "text": "It was exhilarating and elating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29024.0,
      "end_time": 32369.0,
      "text": "but it was also scary and terrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32369.0,
      "end_time": 36595.0,
      "text": "And it got particularly terrifying when we got home from the hospital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36595.0,
      "end_time": 38080.0,
      "text": "and we were unsure"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38080.0,
      "end_time": 42616.0,
      "text": "whether our little baby boy was getting enough nutrients from breastfeeding."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 42616.0,
      "end_time": 45967.0,
      "text": "And we wanted to call our pediatrician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 45967.0,
      "end_time": 48566.0,
      "text": "but we also didn't want to make a bad first impression"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48566.0,
      "end_time": 51054.0,
      "text": "or come across as a crazy, neurotic parent."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51054.0,
      "end_time": 52725.0,
      "text": "So we worried."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52725.0,
      "end_time": 54131.0,
      "text": "And we waited."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 54131.0,
      "end_time": 56450.0,
      "text": "When we got to the doctor's office the next day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56450.0,
      "end_time": 61312.0,
      "text": "she immediately gave him formula because he was pretty dehydrated."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61312.0,
      "end_time": 62770.0,
      "text": "Our son is fine now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62770.0,
      "end_time": 66106.0,
      "text": "and our doctor has reassured us we can always contact her."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 66106.0,
      "end_time": 67656.0,
      "text": "But in that moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67656.0,
      "end_time": 70943.0,
      "text": "I should've spoken up, but I didn't."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70943.0,
      "end_time": 74262.0,
      "text": "But sometimes we speak up when we shouldn't,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74262.0,
      "end_time": 78579.0,
      "text": "and I learned that over 10 years ago when I let my twin brother down."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78579.0,
      "end_time": 81245.0,
      "text": "My twin brother is a documentary filmmaker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81245.0,
      "end_time": 82799.0,
      "text": "and for one of his first films,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 82799.0,
      "end_time": 85438.0,
      "text": "he got an offer from a distribution company."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85438.0,
      "end_time": 86800.0,
      "text": "He was excited,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86800.0,
      "end_time": 89491.0,
      "text": "and he was inclined to accept the offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89491.0,
      "end_time": 91608.0,
      "text": "But as a negotiations researcher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91608.0,
      "end_time": 94585.0,
      "text": "I insisted he make a counteroffer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94585.0,
      "end_time": 97839.0,
      "text": "and I helped him craft the perfect one."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97839.0,
      "end_time": 99544.0,
      "text": "And it was perfect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99544.0,
      "end_time": 102423.0,
      "text": "it was perfectly insulting."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102423.0,
      "end_time": 104160.0,
      "text": "The company was so offended,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104160.0,
      "end_time": 106233.0,
      "text": "they literally withdrew the offer"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106233.0,
      "end_time": 108474.0,
      "text": "and my brother was left with nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108474.0,
      "end_time": 112358.0,
      "text": "And I've asked people all over the world about this dilemma of speaking up:"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112358.0,
      "end_time": 114216.0,
      "text": "when they can assert themselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 114216.0,
      "end_time": 115954.0,
      "text": "when they can push their interests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 115954.0,
      "end_time": 118173.0,
      "text": "when they can express an opinion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 118173.0,
      "end_time": 120887.0,
      "text": "when they can make an ambitious ask."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120887.0,
      "end_time": 125144.0,
      "text": "And the range of stories are varied and diverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125144.0,
      "end_time": 127839.0,
      "text": "but they also make up a universal tapestry."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 127839.0,
      "end_time": 130541.0,
      "text": "Can I correct my boss when they make a mistake?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 130541.0,
      "end_time": 134996.0,
      "text": "Can I confront my coworker who keeps stepping on my toes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134996.0,
      "end_time": 138390.0,
      "text": "Can I challenge my friend's insensitive joke?"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 138390.0,
      "end_time": 142963.0,
      "text": "Can I tell the person I love the most my deepest insecurities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 142963.0,
      "end_time": 145700.0,
      "text": "And through these experiences, I've come to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 145700.0,
      "end_time": 149581.0,
      "text": "that each of us have something called a range of acceptable behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 149581.0,
      "end_time": 154856.0,
      "text": "Now, sometimes we're too strong; we push ourselves too much."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 154856.0,
      "end_time": 156643.0,
      "text": "That's what happened with my brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 156643.0,
      "end_time": 161663.0,
      "text": "Even making an offer was outside his range of acceptable behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 161663.0,
      "end_time": 163211.0,
      "text": "But sometimes we're too weak."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 163211.0,
      "end_time": 165299.0,
      "text": "That's what happened with my wife and I."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 165299.0,
      "end_time": 167539.0,
      "text": "And this range of acceptable behaviors --"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 167539.0,
      "end_time": 170658.0,
      "text": "when we stay within our range, we're rewarded."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 170658.0,
      "end_time": 174851.0,
      "text": "When we step outside that range, we get punished in a variety of ways."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 174851.0,
      "end_time": 178014.0,
      "text": "We get dismissed or demeaned or even ostracized."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178014.0,
      "end_time": 181929.0,
      "text": "Or we lose that raise or that promotion or that deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181929.0,
      "end_time": 184717.0,
      "text": "Now, the first thing we need to know is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 184717.0,
      "end_time": 186744.0,
      "text": "What is my range?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186744.0,
      "end_time": 191265.0,
      "text": "But the key thing is, our range isn't fixed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 191265.0,
      "end_time": 192705.0,
      "text": "it's actually pretty dynamic."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 192705.0,
      "end_time": 197344.0,
      "text": "It expands and it narrows based on the context."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 197344.0,
      "end_time": 202038.0,
      "text": "And there's one thing that determines that range more than anything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 202038.0,
      "end_time": 203355.0,
      "text": "and that's your power."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 203355.0,
      "end_time": 205536.0,
      "text": "Your power determines your range."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 205536.0,
      "end_time": 206997.0,
      "text": "What is power?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 206997.0,
      "end_time": 208788.0,
      "text": "Power comes in lots of forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208788.0,
      "end_time": 211901.0,
      "text": "In negotiations, it comes in the form of alternatives."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211901.0,
      "end_time": 213925.0,
      "text": "So my brother had no alternatives;"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213925.0,
      "end_time": 215136.0,
      "text": "he lacked power."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215136.0,
      "end_time": 216980.0,
      "text": "The company had lots of alternatives;"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 216980.0,
      "end_time": 218170.0,
      "text": "they had power."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 218170.0,
      "end_time": 221254.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it's being new to a country, like an immigrant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 221254.0,
      "end_time": 222737.0,
      "text": "or new to an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 222737.0,
      "end_time": 224320.0,
      "text": "or new to an experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 224320.0,
      "end_time": 226449.0,
      "text": "like my wife and I as new parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 226449.0,
      "end_time": 227974.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it's at work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 227974.0,
      "end_time": 230609.0,
      "text": "where someone's the boss and someone's the subordinate."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 230609.0,
      "end_time": 232317.0,
      "text": "Sometimes it's in relationships,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 232317.0,
      "end_time": 235322.0,
      "text": "where one person's more invested than the other person."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 235322.0,
      "end_time": 238861.0,
      "text": "And the key thing is that when we have lots of power,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 238861.0,
      "end_time": 240714.0,
      "text": "our range is very wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 240714.0,
      "end_time": 243813.0,
      "text": "We have a lot of leeway in how to behave."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 243813.0,
      "end_time": 246537.0,
      "text": "But when we lack power, our range narrows."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 246537.0,
      "end_time": 248947.0,
      "text": "We have very little leeway."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 248947.0,
      "end_time": 251753.0,
      "text": "The problem is that when our range narrows,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 251753.0,
      "end_time": 256310.0,
      "text": "that produces something called the low-power double bind."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256310.0,
      "end_time": 259007.0,
      "text": "The low-power double bind happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 259007.0,
      "end_time": 262576.0,
      "text": "when, if we don't speak up, we go unnoticed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262576.0,
      "end_time": 265359.0,
      "text": "but if we do speak up, we get punished."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 265359.0,
      "end_time": 268094.0,
      "text": "Now, many of you have heard the phrase the \"double bind\""
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 268094.0,
      "end_time": 271065.0,
      "text": "and connected it with one thing, and that's gender."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 271065.0,
      "end_time": 275299.0,
      "text": "The gender double bind is women who don't speak up go unnoticed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 275299.0,
      "end_time": 278127.0,
      "text": "and women who do speak up get punished."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 278127.0,
      "end_time": 283135.0,
      "text": "And the key thing is that women have the same need as men to speak up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 283135.0,
      "end_time": 286004.0,
      "text": "but they have barriers to doing so."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 286004.0,
      "end_time": 289306.0,
      "text": "But what my research has shown over the last two decades"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 289306.0,
      "end_time": 293035.0,
      "text": "is that what looks like a gender difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 293035.0,
      "end_time": 295456.0,
      "text": "is not really a gender double bind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 295456.0,
      "end_time": 297836.0,
      "text": "it's a really a low-power double bind."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 297836.0,
      "end_time": 299744.0,
      "text": "And what looks like a gender difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 299744.0,
      "end_time": 303394.0,
      "text": "are really often just power differences in disguise."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 303394.0,
      "end_time": 306141.0,
      "text": "Oftentimes we see a difference between a man and a woman"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 306141.0,
      "end_time": 307363.0,
      "text": "or men and women,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 307363.0,
      "end_time": 310995.0,
      "text": "and think, \"Biological cause. There's something fundamentally different"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 310995.0,
      "end_time": 312265.0,
      "text": "about the sexes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312265.0,
      "end_time": 314143.0,
      "text": "But in study after study,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 314143.0,
      "end_time": 318893.0,
      "text": "I've found that a better explanation for many sex differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 318893.0,
      "end_time": 320429.0,
      "text": "is really power."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 320429.0,
      "end_time": 323975.0,
      "text": "And so it's the low-power double bind."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 323975.0,
      "end_time": 328815.0,
      "text": "And the low-power double bind means that we have a narrow range,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 328815.0,
      "end_time": 330669.0,
      "text": "and we lack power."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 330669.0,
      "end_time": 331925.0,
      "text": "We have a narrow range,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 331925.0,
      "end_time": 334335.0,
      "text": "and our double bind is very large."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 334335.0,
      "end_time": 336715.0,
      "text": "So we need to find ways to expand our range."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 336715.0,
      "end_time": 338316.0,
      "text": "And over the last couple decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 338316.0,
      "end_time": 341887.0,
      "text": "my colleagues and I have found two things really matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 341887.0,
      "end_time": 346284.0,
      "text": "The first: you seem powerful in your own eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 346284.0,
      "end_time": 349629.0,
      "text": "The second: you seem powerful in the eyes of others."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 349629.0,
      "end_time": 352117.0,
      "text": "When I feel powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 352117.0,
      "end_time": 354016.0,
      "text": "I feel confident, not fearful;"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 354016.0,
      "end_time": 355882.0,
      "text": "I expand my own range."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 355882.0,
      "end_time": 358614.0,
      "text": "When other people see me as powerful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 358614.0,
      "end_time": 361174.0,
      "text": "they grant me a wider range."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 361174.0,
      "end_time": 365952.0,
      "text": "So we need tools to expand our range of acceptable behavior."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 365952.0,
      "end_time": 368367.0,
      "text": "And I'm going to give you a set of tools today."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 368367.0,
      "end_time": 370503.0,
      "text": "Speaking up is risky,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 370503.0,
      "end_time": 375067.0,
      "text": "but these tools will lower your risk of speaking up."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 375067.0,
      "end_time": 380925.0,
      "text": "The first tool I'm going to give you got discovered in negotiations"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 380925.0,
      "end_time": 382329.0,
      "text": "in an important finding."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 382329.0,
      "end_time": 386249.0,
      "text": "On average, women make less ambitious offers"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 386249.0,
      "end_time": 390200.0,
      "text": "and get worse outcomes than men at the bargaining table."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 390200.0,
      "end_time": 393341.0,
      "text": "But Hannah Riley Bowles and Emily Amanatullah have discovered"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 393341.0,
      "end_time": 397043.0,
      "text": "there's one situation where women get the same outcomes as men"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 397043.0,
      "end_time": 399196.0,
      "text": "and are just as ambitious."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 399196.0,
      "end_time": 403251.0,
      "text": "That's when they advocate for others."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 403251.0,
      "end_time": 405412.0,
      "text": "When they advocate for others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 405412.0,
      "end_time": 410313.0,
      "text": "they discover their own range and expand it in their own mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 410313.0,
      "end_time": 411746.0,
      "text": "They become more assertive."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 411746.0,
      "end_time": 415483.0,
      "text": "This is sometimes called \"the mama bear effect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 415483.0,
      "end_time": 417766.0,
      "text": "Like a mama bear defending her cubs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 417766.0,
      "end_time": 422328.0,
      "text": "when we advocate for others, we can discover our own voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 422328.0,
      "end_time": 425469.0,
      "text": "But sometimes, we have to advocate for ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 425469.0,
      "end_time": 426833.0,
      "text": "How do we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 426833.0,
      "end_time": 430862.0,
      "text": "One of the most important tools we have to advocate for ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 430862.0,
      "end_time": 433258.0,
      "text": "is something called perspective-taking."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 433258.0,
      "end_time": 436034.0,
      "text": "And perspective-taking is really simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 436034.0,
      "end_time": 441014.0,
      "text": "it's simply looking at the world through the eyes of another person."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 441014.0,
      "end_time": 444826.0,
      "text": "It's one of the most important tools we have to expand our range."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 444826.0,
      "end_time": 446557.0,
      "text": "When I take your perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 446557.0,
      "end_time": 449020.0,
      "text": "and I think about what you really want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449020.0,
      "end_time": 453461.0,
      "text": "you're more likely to give me what I really want."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 453461.0,
      "end_time": 454985.0,
      "text": "But here's the problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 454985.0,
      "end_time": 457290.0,
      "text": "perspective-taking is hard to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 457290.0,
      "end_time": 458844.0,
      "text": "So let's do a little experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 458844.0,
      "end_time": 461882.0,
      "text": "I want you all to hold your hand just like this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 461882.0,
      "end_time": 463770.0,
      "text": "your finger -- put it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 463770.0,
      "end_time": 468026.0,
      "text": "And I want you to draw a capital letter E on your forehead"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 468026.0,
      "end_time": 472066.0,
      "text": "as quickly as possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 472066.0,
      "end_time": 475407.0,
      "text": "OK, it turns out that we can draw this E in one of two ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 475407.0,
      "end_time": 478916.0,
      "text": "and this was originally designed as a test of perspective-taking."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 478916.0,
      "end_time": 480861.0,
      "text": "I'm going to show you two pictures"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 480861.0,
      "end_time": 482885.0,
      "text": "of someone with an E on their forehead --"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 482885.0,
      "end_time": 485294.0,
      "text": "my former student, Erika Hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 485294.0,
      "end_time": 487286.0,
      "text": "And you can see over here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 487286.0,
      "end_time": 488577.0,
      "text": "that's the correct E."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 488577.0,
      "end_time": 492051.0,
      "text": "I drew the E so it looks like an E to another person."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 492051.0,
      "end_time": 494182.0,
      "text": "That's the perspective-taking E"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 494182.0,
      "end_time": 497261.0,
      "text": "because it looks like an E from someone else's vantage point."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 497261.0,
      "end_time": 500856.0,
      "text": "But this E over here is the self-focused E."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 500856.0,
      "end_time": 502533.0,
      "text": "We often get self-focused."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 502533.0,
      "end_time": 506064.0,
      "text": "And we particularly get self-focused in a crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 506064.0,
      "end_time": 508259.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you about a particular crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 508259.0,
      "end_time": 512285.0,
      "text": "A man walks into a bank in Watsonville, California."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 512284.99999999994,
      "end_time": 514747.99999999994,
      "text": "And he says, \"Give me $2,000,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 514748.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517503.00000000006,
      "text": "or I'm blowing the whole bank up with a bomb.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 517503.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520052.00000000006,
      "text": "Now, the bank manager didn't give him the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 520052.0,
      "end_time": 521873.0,
      "text": "She took a step back."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 521873.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523353.00000000006,
      "text": "She took his perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 523352.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525744.0,
      "text": "and she noticed something really important."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 525744.0,
      "end_time": 528474.0,
      "text": "He asked for a specific amount of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 528474.0,
      "end_time": 530669.0,
      "text": "So she said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 530669.0,
      "end_time": 533265.0,
      "text": "\"Why did you ask for $2,000?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 533265.0,
      "end_time": 535657.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"My friend is going to be evicted"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 535657.0,
      "end_time": 537944.0,
      "text": "unless I get him $2,000 immediately.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 537944.0,
      "end_time": 541018.0,
      "text": "And she said, \"Oh! You don't want to rob the bank --"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 541018.0,
      "end_time": 542530.0,
      "text": "you want to take out a loan.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 542530.0,
      "end_time": 543639.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 543639.0,
      "end_time": 545536.0,
      "text": "\"Why don't you come back to my office,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 545536.0,
      "end_time": 547739.0,
      "text": "and we can have you fill out the paperwork.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 547739.0,
      "end_time": 549214.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 549214.0,
      "end_time": 554276.0,
      "text": "Now, her quick perspective-taking defused a volatile situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 554276.0,
      "end_time": 556119.0,
      "text": "So when we take someone's perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 556119.0,
      "end_time": 561182.0,
      "text": "it allows us to be ambitious and assertive, but still be likable."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 561182.0,
      "end_time": 564474.0,
      "text": "Here's another way to be assertive but still be likable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 564474.0,
      "end_time": 567413.0,
      "text": "and that is to signal flexibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 567413.0,
      "end_time": 571790.0,
      "text": "Now, imagine you're a car salesperson, and you want to sell someone a car."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 571790.0,
      "end_time": 576141.0,
      "text": "You're going to more likely make the sale if you give them two options."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 576141.0,
      "end_time": 577588.0,
      "text": "Let's say option A:"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 577588.0,
      "end_time": 581084.0,
      "text": "$24,000 for this car and a five-year warranty."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 581084.0,
      "end_time": 582701.0,
      "text": "Or option B:"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 582701.0,
      "end_time": 585845.0,
      "text": "$23,000 and a three-year warranty."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 585845.0,
      "end_time": 589447.0,
      "text": "My research shows that when you give people a choice among options,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 589447.0,
      "end_time": 591360.0,
      "text": "it lowers their defenses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 591360.0,
      "end_time": 594202.0,
      "text": "and they're more likely to accept your offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 594202.0,
      "end_time": 596343.0,
      "text": "And this doesn't just work with salespeople;"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 596343.0,
      "end_time": 597558.0,
      "text": "it works with parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 597558.0,
      "end_time": 598861.0,
      "text": "When my niece was four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 598861.0,
      "end_time": 602160.0,
      "text": "she resisted getting dressed and rejected everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 602160.0,
      "end_time": 605079.0,
      "text": "But then my sister-in-law had a brilliant idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 605079.0,
      "end_time": 607654.0,
      "text": "What if I gave my daughter a choice?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 607654.0,
      "end_time": 609699.0,
      "text": "This shirt or that shirt? OK, that shirt."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 609699.0,
      "end_time": 611845.0,
      "text": "This pant or that pant? OK, that pant."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 611845.0,
      "end_time": 613207.0,
      "text": "And it worked brilliantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 613207.0,
      "end_time": 617498.0,
      "text": "She got dressed quickly and without resistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 617498.0,
      "end_time": 619809.0,
      "text": "When I've asked the question around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 619809.0,
      "end_time": 621884.0,
      "text": "when people feel comfortable speaking up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 621884.0,
      "end_time": 623244.0,
      "text": "the number one answer is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 623244.0,
      "end_time": 628022.0,
      "text": "\"When I have social support in my audience; when I have allies.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 628022.0,
      "end_time": 631957.0,
      "text": "So we want to get allies on our side."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 631957.0,
      "end_time": 633841.0,
      "text": "How do we do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 633841.0,
      "end_time": 636034.0,
      "text": "Well, one of the ways is be a mama bear."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 636034.0,
      "end_time": 637534.0,
      "text": "When we advocate for others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 637534.0,
      "end_time": 641087.0,
      "text": "we expand our range in our own eyes and the eyes of others,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 641087.0,
      "end_time": 643806.0,
      "text": "but we also earn strong allies."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 643806.0,
      "end_time": 648537.0,
      "text": "Another way we can earn strong allies, especially in high places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 648537.0,
      "end_time": 651410.0,
      "text": "is by asking other people for advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 651410.0,
      "end_time": 657315.0,
      "text": "When we ask others for advice, they like us because we flatter them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 657315.0,
      "end_time": 659281.0,
      "text": "and we're expressing humility."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 659281.0,
      "end_time": 662831.0,
      "text": "And this really works to solve another double bind."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 662831.0,
      "end_time": 665498.0,
      "text": "And that's the self-promotion double bind."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 665498.0,
      "end_time": 667026.0,
      "text": "The self-promotion double bind"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 667026.0,
      "end_time": 670205.0,
      "text": "is that if we don't advertise our accomplishments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 670205.0,
      "end_time": 671439.0,
      "text": "no one notices."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 671439.0,
      "end_time": 673867.0,
      "text": "And if we do, we're not likable."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 673867.0,
      "end_time": 677457.0,
      "text": "But if we ask for advice about one of our accomplishments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 677457.0,
      "end_time": 682495.0,
      "text": "we are able to be competent in their eyes but also be likeable."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 682495.0,
      "end_time": 684526.0,
      "text": "And this is so powerful"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 684526.0,
      "end_time": 687469.0,
      "text": "it even works when you see it coming."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 687469.0,
      "end_time": 691533.0,
      "text": "There have been multiple times in life when I have been forewarned"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 691533.0,
      "end_time": 696289.0,
      "text": "that a low-power person has been given the advice to come ask me for advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 696289.0,
      "end_time": 698555.0,
      "text": "I want you to notice three things about this:"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 698555.0,
      "end_time": 701930.0,
      "text": "First, I knew they were going to come ask me for advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 701930.0,
      "end_time": 705956.0,
      "text": "Two, I've actually done research on the strategic benefits"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 705956.0,
      "end_time": 707882.0,
      "text": "of asking for advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 707882.0,
      "end_time": 710656.0,
      "text": "And three, it still worked!"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 710656.0,
      "end_time": 711897.0,
      "text": "I took their perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 711897.0,
      "end_time": 714108.0,
      "text": "I became more invested in their cause,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 714108.0,
      "end_time": 718343.0,
      "text": "I became more committed to them because they asked for advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 718343.0,
      "end_time": 721949.0,
      "text": "Now, another time we feel more confident speaking up"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 721949.0,
      "end_time": 724144.0,
      "text": "is when we have expertise."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 724144.0,
      "end_time": 726862.0,
      "text": "Expertise gives us credibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 726862.0,
      "end_time": 729813.0,
      "text": "When we have high power, we already have credibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 729813.0,
      "end_time": 731777.0,
      "text": "We only need good evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 731777.0,
      "end_time": 734771.0,
      "text": "When we lack power, we don't have the credibility."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 734771.0,
      "end_time": 737394.0,
      "text": "We need excellent evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 737394.0,
      "end_time": 741165.0,
      "text": "And one of the ways we can come across as an expert"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 741165.0,
      "end_time": 743784.0,
      "text": "is by tapping into our passion."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 743784.0,
      "end_time": 747982.0,
      "text": "I want everyone in the next few days to go up to friend of theirs"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 747982.0,
      "end_time": 749251.0,
      "text": "and just say to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 749251.0,
      "end_time": 752738.0,
      "text": "\"I want you to describe a passion of yours to me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 752738.0,
      "end_time": 755247.0,
      "text": "I've had people do this all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 755247.0,
      "end_time": 756527.0,
      "text": "and I asked them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 756527.0,
      "end_time": 758720.0,
      "text": "\"What did you notice about the other person"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 758720.0,
      "end_time": 760798.0,
      "text": "when they described their passion?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 760798.0,
      "end_time": 762722.0,
      "text": "And the answers are always the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 762722.0,
      "end_time": 764754.0,
      "text": "\"Their eyes lit up and got big.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 764754.0,
      "end_time": 767727.0,
      "text": "\"They smiled a big beaming smile.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 767727.0,
      "end_time": 769395.0,
      "text": "\"They used their hands all over --"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 769395.0,
      "end_time": 771911.0,
      "text": "I had to duck because their hands were coming at me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 771911.0,
      "end_time": 774136.0,
      "text": "\"They talk quickly with a little higher pitch.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 774136.0,
      "end_time": 775134.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 775134.0,
      "end_time": 777602.0,
      "text": "\"They leaned in as if telling me a secret.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 777602.0,
      "end_time": 778947.0,
      "text": "And then I said to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 778947.0,
      "end_time": 782374.0,
      "text": "\"What happened to you as you listened to their passion?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 782374.0,
      "end_time": 784678.0,
      "text": "They said, \"My eyes lit up."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 784678.0,
      "end_time": 785972.0,
      "text": "I smiled."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 785972.0,
      "end_time": 787369.0,
      "text": "I leaned in.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 787369.0,
      "end_time": 789462.0,
      "text": "When we tap into our passion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 789462.0,
      "end_time": 792852.0,
      "text": "we give ourselves the courage, in our own eyes, to speak up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 792852.0,
      "end_time": 796534.0,
      "text": "but we also get the permission from others to speak up."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 796534.0,
      "end_time": 802533.0,
      "text": "Tapping into our passion even works when we come across as too weak."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 802533.0,
      "end_time": 807344.0,
      "text": "Both men and women get punished at work when they shed tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 807344.0,
      "end_time": 813786.0,
      "text": "But Lizzie Wolf has shown that when we frame our strong emotions as passion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 813786.0,
      "end_time": 820598.0,
      "text": "the condemnation of our crying disappears for both men and women."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 820598.0,
      "end_time": 824090.0,
      "text": "I want to end with a few words from my late father"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 824090.0,
      "end_time": 826675.0,
      "text": "that he spoke at my twin brother's wedding."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 826675.0,
      "end_time": 829664.0,
      "text": "Here's a picture of us."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 829664.0,
      "end_time": 831945.0,
      "text": "My dad was a psychologist like me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 831945.0,
      "end_time": 835691.0,
      "text": "but his real love and his real passion was cinema,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 835691.0,
      "end_time": 836915.0,
      "text": "like my brother."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 836915.0,
      "end_time": 839505.0,
      "text": "And so he wrote a speech for my brother's wedding"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 839505.0,
      "end_time": 842678.0,
      "text": "about the roles we play in the human comedy."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 842678.0,
      "end_time": 844991.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"The lighter your touch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 844991.0,
      "end_time": 849170.0,
      "text": "the better you become at improving and enriching your performance."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 849170.0,
      "end_time": 854001.0,
      "text": "Those who embrace their roles and work to improve their performance"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 854001.0,
      "end_time": 857067.0,
      "text": "grow, change and expand the self."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 857067.0,
      "end_time": 858399.0,
      "text": "Play it well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 858399.0,
      "end_time": 860946.0,
      "text": "and your days will be mostly joyful.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 860946.0,
      "end_time": 862595.0,
      "text": "What my dad was saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 862595.0,
      "end_time": 867048.0,
      "text": "is that we've all been assigned ranges and roles in this world."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 867048.0,
      "end_time": 871005.0,
      "text": "But he was also saying the essence of this talk:"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 871005.0,
      "end_time": 876770.0,
      "text": "those roles and ranges are constantly expanding and evolving."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 876770.0,
      "end_time": 879114.0,
      "text": "So when a scene calls for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 879114.0,
      "end_time": 881251.0,
      "text": "be a ferocious mama bear"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 881251.0,
      "end_time": 883802.0,
      "text": "and a humble advice seeker."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 883802.0,
      "end_time": 887910.0,
      "text": "Have excellent evidence and strong allies."
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 887910.0,
      "end_time": 890770.0,
      "text": "Be a passionate perspective taker."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 890770.0,
      "end_time": 892514.0,
      "text": "And if you use those tools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 892514.0,
      "end_time": 896104.0,
      "text": "and each and every one of you can use these tools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 896104.0,
      "end_time": 899994.0,
      "text": "you will expand your range of acceptable behavior,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 899994.0,
      "end_time": 904082.0,
      "text": "and your days will be mostly joyful."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 904082.0,
      "end_time": 905256.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 905256.0,
      "end_time": 915256.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}